title: YOU DON'T SAY ! -- guest panelists Mel Torme and Pat Carroll
description:
This is the original series that aired on NBC in the 1960s, and 
apparently one of the few existing videotapes that the network didn't erase.

Decades later in the 2000s Saturday Night Live sometimes did a whacked-out
combination spoof of both "PASSWORD" and this game show, in which 
Kristin Wiig's Mindy Grayson character was a panelist in every "Secret Word" sketch.
